Package org.concordion.cubano.data

Data handling utilities.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataCleanup
    Interface for those classes wish to automatically cleanup data, for example data added to database for a test run.

    Class Description
    DataCleanupHelper
    Registration service for data cleanup.
    EntityPool<E>
    Maintains a global pool of of available entities and those that are in use.

    Utility class for reading files.
    JsonLoader
    Utility class for loading JSON files.

    Serialise XMLGregorianCalendar datatype to/from JSON.
